      options: [{ id: `A`, text: `Consisting primarily of letters sent between a taxi driver named Wang Jun and a mysterious woman, Susan Barker's <i>The Incarnations</i> is an epistolary novel.` }, { id: `B`, text: `Susan Barker's novel <i>The Incarnations</i> was published in 2015 and consists primarily of letters.` }, { id: `C`, text: `An epistolary novel is a novel written primarily as a series of fictional documents, such as letters, journal entries, or newspaper clippings.` }, { id: `D`, text: `Published in 2015, <i>The Incarnations</i> is an epistolary novel by English author Susan Barker.` }],
