      options: [{ id: `A`, text: `After exploring nostalgia and Europe's largest shopping mall, Svetlana Boym goes on to discuss various skeptics' takes on the concept of nostalgia.` }, { id: `B`, text: `Svetlana Boym's <i>The Future of Nostalgia</i> provides a multifaceted exploration of nostalgia.` }, { id: `C`, text: `Svetlana Boym explores nostalgia and Europe's largest shopping mall in chapter 8 of her book.` }, { id: `D`, text: `In an exploration of various skeptics' takes on the concept of nostalgia, Svetlana Boym writes, &ldquo;The poethics of nostalgia combines estrangement and human solidarity, affect and reflection.&rdquo;` }],
