      options: [{ id: `A`, text: `Urban grasslands, which are areas of pastures or meadows in cities, benefit cities by increasing diversity among bird species.` }, { id: `B`, text: `Facade-bound green walls enhance air quality, whereas urban grasslands increase diversity among bird species.` }, { id: `C`, text: `Facade-bound green walls and urban grasslands can both be considered urban natural areas.` }, { id: `D`, text: `By enhancing air quality, facade-bound green walls benefit cities.` }],
      answer: `C`,
