      passage: `The 2023 anthology <i>The Big Book of Cyberpunk</i> contains 108 stories. With its chronological scope, it is more comprehensive than the much shorter 1986 anthology <i>Mirrorshades</i>, but <i>Mirrorshades</i>'s careful selection of stories makes that anthology more ______.`,
