      prompt: `Which choice most effectively uses data from the table to complete the statement?`,
      options: [{ id: `A`, text: `participants rated the dog in image 3 as less mature than the dog in image 8 and rated the dog in image 14 as less mature than the dog in image 24.` }, { id: `B`, text: `dogs that participants rated as friendlier were also dogs that participants indicated a stronger willingness to interact with or keep.` }, { id: `C`, text: `the more mature a dog was perceived to be, the more likely participants were to rate it as having light irises.` }, { id: `D`, text: `participants favored the dogs in images 3 and 8, which they rated as less mature than the dogs in images 24 and 14.` }],
